---
title: "Rekakat, the lebanese cheese rolls"
excerpt: "Yallah habibi!"
header:
  image: /assets/images/rekakat.jpg
  teaser: assets/images/rekakat.jpg
---

Ingredients:

* 200g soft goat's cheese
* 1 table spoon of sesame seeds
* 1 table spoon of honey
* spring roll pastry sheet
* neutral oil for frying 

Directions: 

1. In a bowl, mix the cheese, honey, and sesame seeds
2. Add the mixture to your spring roll pastry and roll (close the borders with lukewarm water)
3. Deep fry until golden brown, and enjoy! 
